This is the Perl distribution Hash-Rename.

INSTALLATION

Hash-Rename installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up, you
should just be able to do

    % cpan Hash::Rename

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Hash-Rename documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Hash::Rename

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

